title: City of Baltimore Demographics by Census Tract; Poverty, Labor Force, Income Statistics; 2000
name: City of Baltimore Demographics by Census Tract; Poverty, Labor Force, Income Statistics; 2000
description:
This dataset displays data on specific demographic data from the US 2000 Census by Census Tract in the City of Baltimore. 

The data includes: population of males 16 and over, population of males 16 and over in the labor force, percentage of the male population 16 and over in the labor force and not in the labor force, total population that is below the poverty level, percentage of the population that is below the poverty level, and median household income in 1999.

The data is from the US Census
